      "id": "1-q1",
      "type": "part1",
      "text": "<p><strong>1. “Could we meet for a quick ______?”</strong></p>\n<ol class=\"alpha-paren\">\n<li>independence</li>\n<li>utility</li>\n<li>briefing</li>\n</ol>",
      "keywords": ["could", "meet", "briefing"]
    },
    {
      "id": "1-q2",
      "type": "part1",
      "text": "<p><strong>2. “We ______ the chores.”</strong></p>\n<ol class=\"alpha-paren\">\n<li>preference</li>\n<li>share</li>\n<li>independence</li>\n</ol>",
      "keywords": ["don't", "share", "chores"]
    },
    {
      "id": "1-q3",
      "type": "part1",
      "text": "<p><strong>3. “My ______ is a quiet house.”</strong></p>\n<ol class=\"alpha-paren\">\n<li>respect</li>\n<li>duplicate</li>\n<li>preference</li>\n</ol>",
      "keywords": ["preference", "quiet"]
    },
    {
      "id": "1-q4",
      "type": "part1",
      "text": "<p><strong>4. “The water and electricity ______ are cheap.”</strong></p>\n<ol class=\"alpha-paren\">\n<li>routine</li>\n<li>briefing</li>\n<li>utilities</li>\n<li>clarify</li>\n</ol>",
