    {
      "id": "1-q5",
      "type": "part1",
      "text": "<p><strong>5. “We shop together so we don’t buy ______ food.”</strong></p>\n<ol class=\"alpha-paren\">\n<li>independence</li>\n<li>duplicate</li>\n<li>sharing</li>\n</ol>",
